## Stakeholder Presentation Deck

The stakeholder presentation deck was designed as an executive-style editorial briefing for AtliQ Media leadership.

The deck connects three major election stories into one clear narrative:

* Regional seat distribution shifts
* Constituency-level seat churn
* Margin of victory and electoral competitiveness

The presentation focuses on clean storytelling, neutral analytical framing, and visual communication using Power BI dashboards and data-driven insights.

Key elements included:

* Executive headline
* Supporting analytical stories
* Editorial recommendation
* Data limitations and neutrality notes

The deck was structured specifically for a 5–7 minute stakeholder presentation format.

